    "Significantly, developer satisfaction climbed sharply.",
    "82% of respondents in internal surveys said their boring coding responsibilities made them \"more empowered\" and \"less encumbered\".",
    "While new hires found less onboarding difficulties thanks to AI help, senior engineers appreciated the capabilities for improving their mentoring of younger employees.Still, it wasn't without difficulties.",
    "Not every team adopted the tools with the same passion.",
    "While some felt the suggestions would reduce their coding ability, others were reluctant to believe them."
